show.title: The Officer Fell For Me
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://kukufm.com/show/the-officer-fell-for-me/?utm_source=share_sh
show.description: Lorenzo found Jane's photo in a dead comrade's stuff. He protected her from harassment at the base, thinking she was the comrade's widow. This led to misunderstandings. Jane uncovered a deadly plot. Lorenzo, jealous and deceptive, pushed her away, and she left, tricked by a rival. Believing him missing, she sought revenge but was trapped. Lorenzo rescued her, exposed the plot, and proposed, sealing their war - and betrayal - tested love.
